description:
A Sunday Law is coming. In this riveting, eye-opening video, you will learn the role of the USA in Bible Prophecy! This great nation, ordained by God, will play a powerful part in end-time events. How will this effect you?  How can I receive the seal of God in the last days? These questions and more will be answered in The USA in Bible Prophecy!
